                        <h2 class="post-title-2"><a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/28/south-africas-schools-of-witchcraft-and-wizardry/" title="Permanent Link to South Africa’s schools of witchcraft and wizardry">
                South Africa’s schools of witchcraft and wizardry                </a></h2>
            <div style="clear: both;"></div>

		
            <div class="featured-thumb-wrapper">
			<a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/28/south-africas-schools-of-witchcraft-and-wizardry/" title="Permanent Link to South Africa’s schools of witchcraft and wizardry">
				<img src="http://ivo.co.za/wp-content/uploads/et_temp/IvoVegterWizardHomeopathy-23449_85x85.png" alt='South Africa’s schools of witchcraft and wizardry' width='85px' height='85px' />			</a>
		</div>        
	    		
			<div>
            You wouldn’t be surprised that there are schools of magic in South Africa. After all, someone has to teach would-be astrologers, sangomas and fortune tellers the tricks of the trade. It is more alarming to learn that real universities participate in the charade. Welcome to the Hogwarts Schools at the University of Johannesburg and Durban University of Technology.            </div>
                <a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/28/south-africas-schools-of-witchcraft-and-wizardry/" rel="bookmark" class="readmore" title="Permanent Link to South Africa’s schools of witchcraft and wizardry">
