                        <h2 class="post-title-2"><a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/22/grab-shale-gas-opportunity-but-avoid-opportunism/" title="Permanent Link to Grab shale gas opportunity, but avoid opportunism">
                Grab shale gas opportunity, but avoid opportunism                </a></h2>
            <div style="clear: both;"></div>

		
        		
			<div>
            Now that the election is over, the South African government ought to fast-track shale gas exploration licences, but resist the temptation to be too greedy and authoritarian. A field trip to Canada holds...            </div>
                <a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/22/grab-shale-gas-opportunity-but-avoid-opportunism/" rel="bookmark" class="readmore" title="Permanent Link to Grab shale gas opportunity, but avoid opportunism">
