                        <h2 class="post-title-2"><a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/15/free-markets-as-a-moderate-position/" title="Permanent Link to Free markets as a moderate position">
                Free markets as a moderate position                </a></h2>
            <div style="clear: both;"></div>

		
        		
			<div>
            The misguided idea that free market advocates are on the side of big business is an endless frustration to me. Although they do not oppose business of any size in principle, free markets are usually not in the best interests of big business. They’d rather have protectionism. In that fact lies an important realisation.
            </div>
                <a href="http://ivo.co.za/2014/05/15/free-markets-as-a-moderate-position/" rel="bookmark" class="readmore" title="Permanent Link to Free markets as a moderate position">
    read more 
    </a>
